Importing Data: beaches.csv
```{r}
# rachael cooper
beaches <- read.csv("beaches.csv")
```

Selecting the aes/adding Labels
```{r}
# sarah gould
library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)

beaches<-beaches%>%na.omit()%>%group_by(year)
ggplot(beaches, aes(x=year, y=rainfall))+geom_bar(stat="identity")
```
